<div class="show-page">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="show-banner">
      <div class="col-xs-9 show-background" style= "background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4), rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url('<%= cl_image_path @city.photo %>')";>
        <div class="link-logo show-link-logo">
          <%= link_to root_path do %>
            <h3>v<%= image_tag "world", :class=> "logo-world" %>yagr</h3>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="city-information">
          <h1 class="text-center"><%= @city.name %></h1>
          <div class="info-card hotels">
            <h2>Places to stay</h2>
            <div class="image-and-text">
              <%= cl_image_tag "voyagr/hotel.jpg", width: 350, height: 200 %>

              <p> <%= @hotel["results"][0]["name"] %></p>
              <p> <%= @hotel["results"][0]["vicinity"] %></p>
              <p> <% ref_pic = @hotel["results"][0]["photos"][0]["photo_reference"] %></p>

              <img src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/place/photo?maxwidth=400&photoreference=<%= ref_pic %>&key=AIzaSyClwwweH4aJCRFYX5Q5gEjz8dZ8N6yW574" alt="">
              <!-- <p> <%# @hotel["results"][0]["photos"][0]["photo_reference"] %></p> -->
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        
          <div class="info-card food" >
            <h2>Food</h2>
            <div class="image-and-text">
              <%= cl_image_tag "voyagr/food.jpg", width: 350, height: 200 %>
              <div class="text-and-button">
                <p>Here's a list of places that VoyagrBot thinks you might enjoy eating. As a robot he doesn't know a great deal about food and drink so he's stolen these suggestions from elsewhere.</p>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#foodModal">Food & Drink</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        
          <div class="info-card entertainment">
            <h2>Entertainment</h2>
            <div class="image-and-text">
              <%= cl_image_tag "voyagr/entertainment.jpg", width: 350, height: 200 %>
              <div class="text-and-button">
                <p>VoyagrBot recommends these places for you to entertain yourself while exploring <%= @city.name %>. These are places which should be uniquely suited to you, based on your answers.</p>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#entertainmentModal">Entertainment</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        
          <div class="info-card sightseeing">
          <h2>Sightseeing</h2>
            <div class="image-and-text">
              <%= cl_image_tag "voyagr/sightseeing.jpg", width: 350, height: 200 %>
              <div class="text-and-button">
                <p>Below is a list of places which VoyagrBot suggests that you might enjoy looking at with your human eyeballs. Thanks VoyagrBot, you friendly little bundle of code and errors you. </p>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#sightseeingModal">Sightseeing</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="col-xs-3 show-map">
      <div id="map" style="width: 100%; height: 100vh;" data-markers="<%= @markers.to_json %>">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="hotelModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
          <h4 class="modal-title">Places to rest your head</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          <div class="suggestion">
